OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter football players injured
OL,6,FA man has been charged with five
OL,7,Fcounts of attempted murder after a hit-
OL,8,Fand-run in Arnold which has left a man
OL,9,F"fighting for his life."
OL,11,FIt's after three members of Woodthorpe
OL,12,FPark Rangers FC were injured after a
OL,13,Fred Vauxhall Astra mounted a kerb and
OL,14,Fstruck a group of people on Saturday
OL,15,Fmorning (May 9).
OL,17,FA 40-year-old man was arrested later
OL,18,Fthat same day.
OL,20,FCounter terrorism police have not been
OL,21,Finvolved in the investigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
