OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778529954
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter football players injured
OL,6,FDuane Anthony of Marton Road, Chilwell
OL,7,Fhas now been charged with multiple
OL,8,Foffences, including five counts of
OL,9,Fattempted murder.
OL,11,FHe has also been charged with
OL,12,Faggravated vehicle taking, driving
OL,13,Fwhilst disqualified and driving
OL,14,Fwithout valid insurance.
OL,16,FAnthony appeared at Nottingham
OL,17,FMagistrates Court this morning.
OL,19,FDetective Chief Inspector Ruby Burrow,
OL,20,Fwho is leading the investigation for
OL,21,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778529954
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter football players injured
OL,6,F"As we share today's news, our
OL,7,Fthoughts remain with those affected by
OL,8,Fthis incident, in particular the man
OL,9,Fwho sustained life-threatening
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,F"The victims and their families have
OL,13,Fbeen updated on today's charging
OL,14,Fdecision, which we hope will provide
OL,15,Fsome small degree of comfort at this
OL,16,Fdifficult time.
OL,18,F"This was a shocking incident that
OL,19,Fwill have been incredibly distressing
OL,20,Ffor all those involved and anyone who
OL,21,Fwitnessed it happen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778529954
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter football players injured
OL,6,F"On that note, I'd ask people to
OL,7,Fplease not speculate about this
OL,8,Fincident, online or otherwise, as
OL,9,Fdoing so could potentially impede the
OL,10,Fpursuit of justice.
OL,12,F"As our investigation continues, I
OL,13,Fwould like to thank the entire
OL,14,Finvestigation team, who worked around
OL,15,Fthe clock throughout the weekend to
OL,16,Fhelp secure these charges."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@[O]
